summary: Stans need to stop acting like they’re faves have NEVER lipsynced. It’s vey common in kpop but that doesn’t mean the idols can’t...
body:
Stans need to stop acting like they’re faves have NEVER lipsynced. It’s vey common in kpop but that doesn’t mean the idols can’t sing. They might just not have been feeling it that day or maybe the station requires it (idk) so 1. Don’t act like they’ve never done it and 2. Don’t act like they can’t sing just cause they have lipsynced

Edit: some people have reblogged good points saying some idols also do it because they haven’t mastered singing and dancing because obviously that’s gonna make your voice sound weird, the microphones could malfunction or some idols could be sick but still have to perform but they aren’t able to
